     The Pathing has changed in GFay dramatically, seemingly to keep new players alive.   Mobs no longer pursue you to the Guards, but will veer off wel before them.<br>
<br>
      Running toward Guard Brookrock at the &quot;newb lift&quot; will cause the monsters to veer off and take the trail over to the  toward the POD Lift, where the guards will waste them.<br>
<br>
      Running to the Orc Lift from CB, the Mobs will take off into the woods to the left (if your looking toward the lift) and run hither and yon, keeping you on the agro list- not uncommon now to see someone, thinking they are safe, stroll back to Orc hill and get pummeled by a ton of stuff that usually would have been killed by the Guards.<br>
<br>
      Sadly, this does affect pets, and they will take off just the same, Enchanters are having a really rough time there right now as pets &quot;vanish&quot; and wander around the zone for a while.<br>
<br>
      Seems to me the whole game has become &quot;dumb&quot; all of a sudden.  Leveled 2 alts in Paladul caverns, the first one died at least 12 times in the Bandit camps, the 2nd not even once-  the Bandits seemed very tame and the usual &quot;tension&quot; and excitement was not there. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showMessageRange?topicID=4770.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a> <b>2</b>  </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showPrevMessage?topicID=4770.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showNextMessage?topicID=4770.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4770.topic&index=29><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/classic/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.threadControl?topicID=4770.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=4770.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies"> Click to receive email notification of replies</a> <br>  <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=4770.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/unsubscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to stop receiving email notification of replies"> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies</a> <br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><fo